Karl Pilkington is a Sony Award-winning, Emmy Award-nominated radio producer, best known for starring in An Idiot Abroad and producing and cohosting The Ricky Gervais Show on the radio and later in the form of podcasts and an HBO television show. He is the author of Happyslapped by a Jellyfish, An Idiot Abroad, Karlology, and Ricky Gervais Presents: The World of Karl Pilkington.
